page.download.description.message: Download the latest version of Invero Minecraft GUI plugin

轻松创建高度自定义的 Minecraft GUI 插件.message: Easily create highly customizable Minecraft GUI plugins

features.1.description.message: Invero greatly reducing complexity and redundancy in the configuration process. Ideal for users who want to achieve their goals quickly and effortlessly.

features.2.description.message: Invero is an incredibly powerful GUI plugin designed for a wide range of scenarios. It enables users to bring their ideas to life and create amazing plugin-level experiences.

features.3.description.message: Invero offers seamless compatibility with a broad range of popular plugins, providing developers with an API to expand even more  features. It's also an open-source project on GitHub.

features.4.description.message: Efficient rendering mechanism ensures smooth user experience

features.5.description.message: Compatible with multiple Minecraft versions, adapting to different environments

site.home.description.message: Invero - Easily create highly customizable Minecraft GUI plugins
